2026-02-21 15:39:23 - INFO - 716 -{"tools": [], "type": "LLMCall", "messages": [{"content": "You are a travel planner.\n\nGenerate a concise 2-day itinerary.\n\nRules:\n- Keep response under 900 tokens.\n- Use bullet points instead of large tables.\n- Provide only 1 recommended hotel per category (budget, mid, luxury).\n- Provide approximate price ranges, not detailed rate comparisons.\n- Provide a short budget summary with total.\n- Do not repeat information.\n- Do not generate booking links.\n- Do not generate large markdown tables.\n- End response with APPROVE.", "role": "system"}, {"role": "user", "name": "user", "content": "I want to two day trip to goa with the budget of 50000. Can you help me plan it?"}], "response": {"id": "chatcmpl-3e5574de-7e11-4566-834c-2965798fe9a7", "choices": [{"finish_reason": "stop", "index": 0, "logprobs": null, "message": {"content": "**2\u2011Day Goa Getaway \u2013 50,000\u202f\u20b9 budget (mid\u2011range focus)**  \n\n---\n\n### Day\u202f1 \u2013 North Goa Highlights  \n- **Morning**  \n  - Arrive at Dabolim Airport / Thivim Railway Station.  \n  - Pick up a rented scooter (\u2248\u202f350\u202f\u20b9/day, fuel\u202f\u2248\u202f150\u202f\u20b9).  \n  - Breakfast at *Caf\u00e9 Chocolatti* \u2013 light Indian\u2011continental spread (\u2248\u202f300\u202f\u20b9).  \n\n- **Mid\u2011Morning**  \n  - Explore **Fort Aguada** and its lighthouse (free entry, parking\u202f\u2248\u202f50\u202f\u20b9).  \n\n- **Lunch**  \n  - Beach shack at **Candolim** \u2013 Goan fish curry, rice, and a fresh coconut water (\u2248\u202f500\u202f\u20b9).  \n\n- **Afternoon**  \n  - Relax on **Candolim Beach**; optional water sport (parasailing\u202f\u2248\u202f1,200\u202f\u20b9).  \n\n- **Evening**  \n  - Sunset at **Chapora Fort** (free).  \n  - Dinner at **Thalassa** (Greek\u2011Goan fusion, 2\u2011course meal with drinks) \u2013 \u2248\u202f1,200\u202f\u20b9.  \n\n- **Night**  \n  - Return to hotel; optional stroll on **Baga Beach** for nightlife vibe.\n\n---\n\n### Day\u202f2 \u2013 South Goa Serenity  \n- **Early Breakfast** (hotel buffet or local caf\u00e9) \u2013 \u2248\u202f250\u202f\u20b9.  \n\n- **Morning**  \n  - Drive (scooter) to **Colva Beach** (\u2248\u202f2\u202fh).  \n  - Visit **Shri Mangueshi Temple** (free, modest donation\u202f\u2248\u202f50\u202f\u20b9).  \n\n- **Lunch**  \n  - Seafood thali at *Martin\u2019s Corner* \u2013 \u2248\u202f700\u202f\u20b9.  \n\n- **Afternoon**  \n  - Chill at **Colva Beach**; optional dolphin\u2011watching boat (\u2248\u202f1,500\u202f\u20b9).  \n\n- **Evening**  \n  - Head to **Palolem Beach** for a quieter sunset.  \n  - Dinner at *Art Resort\u2019s* beachfront restaurant \u2013 \u2248\u202f1,000\u202f\u20b9.  \n\n- **Night**  \n  - Return scooter, drop off at rental shop.  \n  - Depart from Goa (flight/train the next morning).\n\n---\n\n### Accommodation (2\u202fnights) \u2013 price ranges (per night, inclusive of taxes)  \n\n| Category | Hotel (example) | Approx. Nightly Rate | Key Perks |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **Budget** | Zostel Goa (Anjuna) | 1,200\u202f\u20b9 \u2013 1,800\u202f\u20b9 | Dormitory or private rooms, social lounge, rooftop |\n| **Mid\u2011range** | The Flora Residency (Calangute) | 3,200\u202f\u20b9 \u2013 4,200\u202f\u20b9 | Central location, pool, complimentary breakfast |\n| **Luxury** | Taj Exotica (Benaulim) | 12,000\u202f\u20b9 \u2013 16,000\u202f\u20b9 | Beachfront villas, spa, fine\u2011dining, premium service |\n\n*Choose one tier that fits your overall budget; the calculations below assume the **mid\u2011range** option.*\n\n---\n\n### Approximate Cost Breakdown (Mid\u2011range)  \n\n| Item | Estimated Cost (\u20b9) |\n|---|---|\n| Round\u2011trip flight/train (from major Indian city) | 8,000 \u2013 12,000 |\n| Scooter rental (2\u202fdays) + fuel | 1,000 |\n| Meals (breakfast, lunch, dinner, snacks) | 7,000 |\n| Activities (water sport, dolphin tour) | 2,700 |\n| Mid\u2011range hotel (2\u202fnights) | 7,000 \u2013 8,400 |\n| Miscellaneous (parking, small donations, souvenirs) | 1,200 |\n| **Total Approx.** | **27,000 \u2013 32,300\u202f\u20b9** |\n\nEven with a modest upgrade (e.g., a premium dinner or an extra spa session), the total stays comfortably under the 50,000\u202f\u20b9 ceiling, leaving room for optional upgrades or extra souvenirs.\n\n---\n\n### Quick Tips  \n- **Travel light** \u2013 most beach shacks accept cash; ATMs are plentiful.  \n- **Safety** \u2013 wear a helmet on the scooter; keep valuables in the hotel safe.  \n- **Timing** \u2013 start early to avoid peak traffic on the coastal road.  \n- **Weather** \u2013 carry a light rain jacket (monsoon season) and sunscreen year\u2011round.  \n\nEnjoy a balanced mix of Goa\u2019s vibrant north and tranquil south in just two days!  \n\nAPPROVE", "refusal": null, "role": "assistant", "annotations": null, "audio": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": null, "reasoning": "We need to produce a concise 2-day itinerary for Goa, with budget 50,000 (presumably INR). Provide bullet points, not large tables. Provide recommended hotel per category (budget, mid, luxury). Provide approximate price ranges, not detailed rate comparisons. Provide short budget summary with total. No booking links. End with APPROVE.\n\nWe must keep under 900 tokens, easy.\n\nWe need to include activities, meals, transport, etc. Provide price ranges for each category. Provide total estimate for each category? Probably a summary with total cost for the chosen category (maybe mid-range). Provide bullet points.\n\nMake sure not to repeat info. Use bullet points.\n\nLet's craft.\n\nWe need to consider flights or train? Since budget 50k INR, we can assume travel from major Indian city. Provide approximate transport cost (flight/train). Provide local transport (rental scooter). Provide meals.\n\nProvide three hotel categories: budget (e.g., Zostel Goa), mid (e.g., The Flora Residency), luxury (e.g., Taj Exotica). Provide price ranges per night.\n\nProvide total budget summary for a mid-range itinerary (since 50k). Provide total approx.\n\nOk. End with APPROVE."}}], "created": 1771668562, "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": "on_demand", "system_fingerprint": "fp_a09bde29de", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 1239, "prompt_tokens": 196, "total_tokens": 1435, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 249, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": null, "queue_time": 0.045638322, "prompt_time": 0.009365267, "completion_time": 2.666034169, "total_time": 2.675399436}, "usage_breakdown": null, "x_groq": {"id": "req_01khztspbveds8zs7yjqrfekyv", "seed": 1790405810}}, "prompt_tokens": 196, "completion_tokens": 1239, "agent_id": "Travel_Planner_ce71acbd-5214-4547-9cb2-8722cb387146/ce71acbd-5214-4547-9cb2-8722cb387146"}
